OL,3,CReturning after a deadly war: Can
OL,4,CSyria rebuild for a new generation?
OL,6,FWords by ITV News Producer Michael
OL,7,FMaitland-Jones
OL,9,F"I lived before in a tent, then when
OL,10,Four hometown was liberated, we moved
OL,11,Fback. It was fully destroyed."
OL,13,FSiham, a seventh-grade student, is
OL,14,Fspeaking from her classroom in a
OL,15,Frefurbished school in Idlib.
OL,17,FShe is surrounded by many like her -
OL,18,FSyrian children who, in the months
OL,19,Fsince the Assad regime fell, have
OL,20,Freturned from vast refugee camps to
OL,21,Fwhat is left of their homes.
