OL,3,CReturning after a deadly war: Can
OL,4,CSyria rebuild for a new generation?
OL,6,FAccording to the UNHCR, around 1.8
OL,7,Fmillion internally displaced Syrians
OL,8,Fhave now returned.
OL,10,F"We live now in my uncle's home while
OL,11,Fwe are fixing our home," says Siham.
OL,13,F"I live with my mother, my father
OL,14,Fdied... my father wanted to travel to
OL,15,FLebanon, but the regime army detained
OL,16,Fhim and killed him."
OL,18,FDespite the trauma her family have
OL,19,Fbeen through, she is hopeful for the
OL,20,Ffuture, saying she is glad to be back
OL,21,Fin school.
