OL,6,FThe one she now studies at was rebuilt
OL,7,Fby the NGO, Basmeh and Zeitooneh,
OL,8,Fafter being destroyed in the civil war.
OL,10,FThe education of children like her
OL,11,Falso represents a test for a
OL,12,Fgovernment that is still just over a
OL,13,Fyear old.
OL,15,FSince she returned to school on
OL,16,FSeptember 21, she has been learning
OL,17,Funder an educational framework that is
OL,18,Fbeing rolled out across Syrian schools
OL,19,Ffor the first time in over a decade.
