OL,3,CReturning after a deadly war: Can
OL,4,CSyria rebuild for a new generation?
OL,6,FEducating a new generation of Syrians
OL,7,Fremains an immense task, however.
OL,9,FOne in three schools in Syria is still
OL,10,Funusable - either damaged, destroyed,
OL,11,For converted into shelter, while 2.4
OL,12,Fmillion children remain out of school
OL,13,Fnationwide, according to UNICEF.
OL,15,FInstability in parts of the country
OL,16,Fhas also had a knock-on effect in some
OL,17,Fschools.
