OL,3,CReturning after a deadly war: Can
OL,4,CSyria rebuild for a new generation?
OL,6,FViolent clashes between multiple
OL,7,Ffactions in Syria's Southern province
OL,8,Fof Sweida have led to nearly 200,000
OL,9,Fpeople being displaced, according to
OL,10,Fthe NGO Action for Humanity.
OL,12,FIn a school in Daraa, in Southwestern
OL,13,FSyria, a teacher speaks about the
OL,14,Fimpact of the crisis.
OL,16,F"We don't have enough desks after we
OL,17,Freceived more students from Sweida...
OL,18,Fthe students have doubled this year,"
OL,19,Fthey said.
