OL,6,F"The displaced families who come are
OL,7,Falready very poor families.. the
OL,8,Fschool's building needs a lot of
OL,9,Frepairs, it lacks doors and windows
OL,10,Fwhile the winter is coming."
OL,12,FOutside in the school courtyard,
OL,13,Fchildren play games and laugh, but
OL,14,Fsigns of strain show through in the
OL,15,Fpacked classrooms and peeling walls.
