OL,3,CReturning after a deadly war: Can
OL,4,CSyria rebuild for a new generation?
OL,6,FThe estimated cost of rebuilding post-
OL,7,Fwar Syria is $216 billion, according
OL,8,Fto the World Bank - nearly three times
OL,9,Fthe estimated amount for Gaza.
OL,11,FIn November, Syria's President Ahmed
OL,12,FAl Sharaa went on a global tour that
OL,13,Fsaw him meet US President Donald
OL,14,FTrump, with part of his mission being
OL,15,Fto improve economic ties.
OL,17,FThe new Syrian administration has
OL,18,Ffaced criticism, not least during
OL,19,FMarch when hundreds of the country's
OL,20,FAlawite minority were killed in
OL,21,Fclashes.
