OL,3,CReturning after a deadly war: Can
OL,4,CSyria rebuild for a new generation?
OL,6,FFighting has also recently broken out
OL,7,Fin Aleppo between the Syrian army and
OL,8,FKurdish groups, with thousands forced
OL,9,Fto flee.
OL,11,FDespite optimism from some about
OL,12,FSyria's new government, the marks of
OL,13,Fover a decade of civil war still
OL,14,Fremain across much of the country.
OL,16,FThe government's ability to rebuild
OL,17,Fand provide for ordinary Syrians will
OL,18,Fprove a decisive test.
